gnu.xml
Class ElementType

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--gnu.xml.ElementType
public class ElementType
extends java.lang.Object

Name and type information for an element tag in a given namespace. If DTDs or XML Schemas are implemented, the "type" of an element should be a sub-class of the class, but for now, all we do is handle name, though in a namespace-aware way.
